{"tid":1601082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］十二和你SHOP前線感謝祭——前線休息 八方支援","createTime":"2019-09-29T01:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T05:39:58.000Z","uid":124536,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3a44501c79596ea98ee3d6cd616076f5335f71","tid":1601082,"uid":124536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sz797zh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsz797zh.jpg&h=9c21f9f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟緊十一我哋嘅義士準備要征戰沙場，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢場將會係一場前所未見嘅苦戰。</span></strong>我地未必個個都敢上前線，可以好似前線手足咁勇敢，為咗香港嘅未來，就算害怕都行出嚟為大家擋子彈。但我哋係咪可以做多啲嘢，為前線手足分擔佢哋嘅重擔呢？<br />\n<br />\n經過十一漫長嘅苦戰，我相信我哋第二日冇可能有心情照常生活，咁係因為我哋已經係梁繼平所講嘅「共同體」&mdash;「能想像他人痛苦，並且甘願彼此分擔的群體」。十一義士為我哋拋頭顱灑熱血，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">十二係時候到我哋接力</span></strong>，延續對準政權及其爪牙嘅戰鬥，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>俾手足好好休息。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，我提議十月二號我哋一齊去唔同嘅黨鐵商場，繼續揸緊黨鐵春袋。</span></strong>雖然塞商場係絕對無辨法同前線手足嘅戰鬥相比，但我希望每一位因為各種理由而無法上前線嘅人，都可以盡一分微力去支援手足，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾前線手足知道佢哋唔係孤軍作軍！</span></strong>我哋要不分和勇、齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n同時，呢個亦都係一個好機會俾我哋去感謝手足嘅無私奉獻。唔知大家仲記唔記得八月沙田新城市義士凱旋而歸、市民鼓掌致敬嘅畫面呢？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我希望我哋可以一齊行出嚟重現八月義士凱旋而歸嘅一幕</span></strong>，俾前線手足知道我哋好感謝佢哋每一個人；知道佢哋嘅努力同犧牲我哋全部都睇得見；知道我哋亦絕對唔會忘記佢哋嘅付出！<br />\n<br />\n行動細節，大家一齊諗！小弟拋磚引玉：<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵商場：新城市、德福、綠楊坊（大家一齊再諗）<br />\n時間：12:00開始<br />\n活動（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不玩膠</span></strong>）：塞美心、藍商鋪，默站靜坐，演奏、齊唱國歌、勇武進行曲（不唱肥媽），寫信、心意卡畀在囚、流亡義士，宣讀感謝前線宣言（如有），貼寫上感謝字句嘅連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WE WILL FIGHT FOR HONG KONG! WE WILL STAND WITH HONG KONG!</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3AUprJLA7w&amp;list=LLeWtm2xOvVcBEe-ycI-M0Sw&amp;index=2&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv3AUprJLA7w%26list%3DLLeWtm2xOvVcBEe-ycI-M0Sw%26index%3D2%26t%3D0s&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=2432ca44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3AUprJLA7w&amp;list=LLeWtm2xOvVcBEe-ycI-M0Sw&amp;index=2&amp;t=0s</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">感謝前線手足　勇武救港　身土不二<br />\n<br />\n祝　武運昌隆</span></strong>"},{"pid":"62962f4be546771d20f96f25dfa7622889d79eb9","tid":1601082,"uid":124536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:42:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85da1151bc62cb3b9b14276c07a4b9b4ab7a30e8","tid":1601082,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:43:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人！！<br />\n<br />\n政府已經怕左美國人權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係度扮會回應普選訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔好忘記共產黨係信唔過既盜國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有香港自治/香港獨立先可以得到5大訴求！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />929 全球反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />101 慶佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港自治，主權在民！<br />\n拯救香港，打倒共黨！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港獨立，還政於民！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8a4649dfabbfeb05e4a9876f53ef44abb6c9370","tid":1601082,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:45:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e896dfc102a23d4d78837e6aa9d9bf88c