法<br />\n仆街感謝祭都比你諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36509b1413dbea9a33de7d42cf13fb4674940ded","tid":1601082,"uid":124536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:15:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9872a1bcb160d73ab0dc75a2871e39a1c1d4e63c","tid":1601082,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df7027226a77af3c794045ed317cc0885a339df","tid":1601082,"uid":124536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d93d4a9abff3b2262ffc1fb07353eabe91bb748e","tid":1601082,"uid":124536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"053d3fd7e90ff5806b7c608d303e1db1a7a174fd","tid":1601082,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ecdc1216ad3dae747a693c7a069e85157a2b5b","tid":1601082,"uid":124536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:04:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bec664bb4f046f002ebddf62e7192911cd7282e","tid":1601082,"uid":267623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPush"},{"pid":"b5095ae91b2d1b62ab04761382325fe0a7d42219","tid":1601082,"uid":124536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:32:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3aa971a4f3e2ef08a70bcab149d33e2f699c6940","tid":1601082,"uid":264536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"前線感謝祭！！巴打你真係好幽默！！"